  "detailed_description": "<h1>Third Party Support</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Steam Deck Partial support.<br></li><li> Tobii Eye Tracker for Avatar head and eyes.<br></li><li> 5 Additional tracked body points supported, Vive trackers or Kinect plugins for SteamVR.<br></li><li> Razer Chroma (soon)<br></li><li> Vive Face Tracker.<br><br><br><br></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Helios is, at it's core, a creator friendly Social Desktop + VR game made in Unreal Engine 5.<br><br>Helios offers a more immersive, interactive, and creator friendly experience than anything currently available.<br><br>You can create and explore community created virtual worlds with friends or you can join others in public or private servers, create and share avatars all through Mod.Io.<br><br>Helios harnesses the vast capabilities of the Unreal Engine, empowering creators in new ways along with unparalleled visual fidelity.<br><br>As the community grows, more activities that we haven't even considered will begin to emerge organically.<br><br>Our mission is to make it as simple as possible for users to add their unique content via Unreal Engine.",
  "about_the_game": "Helios is, at it's core, a creator friendly Social Desktop + VR game made in Unreal Engine 5.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHelios offers a more immersive, interactive, and creator friendly experience than anything currently available.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can create and explore community created virtual worlds with friends or you can join others in public or private servers, create and share avatars all through Mod.Io.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHelios harnesses the vast capabilities of the Unreal Engine, empowering creators in new ways along with unparalleled visual fidelity.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs the community grows, more activities that we haven't even considered will begin to emerge organically.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur mission is to make it as simple as possible for users to add their unique content via Unreal Engine.",
